Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:32.30,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:34.83,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,He’s being consumed by evil energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:37.00,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,At this rate Mega Man will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,0:00:57.77,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,If you haven’t been\Nconsumed by evil energy yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:00:59.40,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,this will save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:10.70,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,Mega Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:13.26,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,I can see within your heart…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:02:01.66,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,You’ve been working this hard…\Nall for the sake of justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.57,0:02:08.77,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,If you’re here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:11.77,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,then this planet is already safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:22.43,Default,Proto Man,0,0,0,,What happened to Mega Man!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:23.83,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,He’s alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.86,0:02:26.00,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,He’ll wake up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:28.37,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,My work here is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:30.90,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,We probably won’t meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.93,0:02:33.06,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,I leave Mega Man to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:40.33,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,I forgot one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:44.63,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,Sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:45.66,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,but I have a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:49.40,Default,Roll,0,0,0,,Mega Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:51.80,Default,Roll,0,0,0,,Stay strong, Mega Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:56.40,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Roll...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:02:59.40,Default,Roll,0,0,0,,Mega Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:02.06,Default,Auto,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:05.93,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,I’m alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:08.17,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:10.80,Default,Dr. Light,0,0,0,,Duo saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:13.66,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Duo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:21.33,Default,Proto Man,0,0,0,,If it’s about Duo, he already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:23.60,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Proto Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:27.46,Default,Proto Man,0,0,0,,Mega Man, he entrusted\Nme with this message.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:29.77,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,From Duo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:30.66,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:35.33,Default,Proto Man,0,0,0,,He said, ‘Thank you.’
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:38.40,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Duo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:44.06,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:52.86,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Thank you, Duo...
